title: DSC106 Profolio
description: Personal Profolio Website based on HTML and JS. This is an ongoing project so it is still under development.

title: Zoo-Seeker App
description: An Android Application using Android Studio and Google Map API. It generates an efficient visit route according to user location and chosen “want-to-go” exhibits list in San Diego Zoo.

title: Self-Driving Car
description: Built a self-driving car with lane detection using Raspberry Pi. Implemented QR Code recognition to perform stop and turn instruction

title: Health Care ChatBot
description: Cross-platform application using Expo that provides users with easy and fast access to Chatbot services.

title: Context Encoder Reimplementation
description: Pytorch training network from scratch, generates predictions on masked areas from image datasets.
